{c_label}Cooldown: {/c}{c_resource}{Cooldown Time}{/c} seconds
Varyana swings two axes in an arc in front of her, dealing {if:SF_11}{c_number}{payload:DAMAGE}{/c}{else}moderate{/if} Physical damage and {if:SF_11}{c_number}{dot:BASIC_BLEED_TOOLTIP}{/c}{else}minor{/if} Bleeding damage over {c_number}{buffduration:BLEED_BUFF}{/c} seconds.

Selecting a Mercenary Core Skill alters their wielded Weapon and Basic Attack.
{c_label}Weapon:{/c} {c_important}Dual Axes{/c}
{c_label}Basic Attack:{/c} {c_important}Double Strike{/c}
Varyana slashes enemies with dual axes, dealing {if:SF_11}{c_number}{payload:MELEE_PAYLOAD_TOOLTIP}{/c}{else}moderate{/if} Physical damage. She has a {c_number}[{SF_7}*100]%{/c} chance to also deal {if:SF_11}{c_number}{dot:BASIC_BLEED_TOOLTIP}{/c}{else}minor{/if} Bleeding damage over {c_number}{SF_8}{/c} seconds.
